 calibration lines along with a broadband reduction of the midfrequency\nnoise floor. The observed increase in the astrophysical range and a reduction\nin the occurrence of nonastrophysical transients suggest that the above method\nis a viable data cleaning technique for current and future generation\ngravitational wave observatories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Jan 2020 17:10:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 28 May 2020 14:08:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-29"}
