mance with the state-of-the-art systems, and both dependency information\nand prior knowledge play important roles in CDR extraction task.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Jan 2020 02:24:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-03"}
